===Etymology===
地 (ち, chi) "ground" + 下 (か, ka) "under"

===Noun===
[[Category:Japanese nouns|ちか]]
'''地下''' ([[ちか]], [[chika]])
#[[underground]]

====Idioms====
*地下に<br>ちかに<br>''chika ni''<br>in the [[grave]]<br><br>
*地下に潜る<br>ちかにもぐる<br>''chika ni moguru''<br>go underground (as in a political movement)

